Processes fluids by reducing them to solid components or treating them with a selected filter.
Every slot has its own production time.

Head Lift: 10 meters.(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)

Has a single belt output which outputs the solid products in a set order.

This fixed output order can be sorted with splitter trees or a smart sorting system.
